title: IMPOSTORS - Among Us Song
author: Shiloh & Bros
description:
This is part of our If Everything Was Like Among Us videos! We're so excited for the new Airships map. Who else thinks Among Us in real life would be so cool! 🙋‍♀️

Thank you to the Portland Spirit for letting us film on their boat! https://www.portlandspirit.com

Thanks to Cooper Grey from She's Alaska for helping us with this song! His channel https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCcveoEbcHSG8M_uhWmJAhkg

If you like  The Norris Nuts, Dixie D'Amelio, or the Txunamy, you'll love our channel. We do funny pranks, songs, and skits!

Shiloh's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/shilohanelson/

Song credits: 
Songwriters: Cooper Grey (from She’s Alaska), Shiloh & Bros, Elijah Nelson, Shiloh Nelson, Britney Nelson
Track Production, Mixing and Mastering: Diego Fernandes

Subscribe here! http://bit.ly/ShilohToJudahChannel

Hit the bell to be notified when we post new videos!
